### Experimental API Tests
### Tests for ExperimentalController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096

### Create workspace
### Creates a new experimental workspace
POST http://localhost:8080/api/experimental/workspace
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "my-experimental-workspace",
  "path": "/projects/my-project"
}

###

### Get worktree info
### Returns information about the current worktree
GET http://localhost:8080/api/experimental/worktree
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create worktree
### Creates a new git worktree
POST http://localhost:8080/api/experimental/worktree
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branch": "feature/new-feature",
  "path": "/projects/my-project-worktree"
}

###

### Remove worktree
### Removes an existing git worktree
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/experimental/worktree
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "/projects/my-project-worktree"
}

###
